{"tid":1021713,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"肩之情人節生日大餐","createTime":"2019-02-14T12:16:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T07:49:30.000Z","uid":78683,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e37ccd7e204d78b4a153c4a74e657740863da492","tid":1021713,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T12:16:41.000Z","msg":"其實都過第27年單身生日嘅情人節 麻木咗了<br />\n仲要今日有啲唔舒服 無乜胃口<br />\n但海皇呢個「很想獨自快樂餐」<br />\n根本為今日嘅我而推出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hCUj0vT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhCUj0vT.png&h=bb65f647&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好似好豐富咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後都係外賣返屋企食 太多人 又要等位<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SRQLbCW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSRQLbCW.png&h=0cfd5ca1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n單身萬歲碎牛肉 啲牛肉少到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RnRePp1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRnRePp1.png&h=eb408d8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n很堅強齋腸 完全係靠甜醬 食咗半兜無晒甜醬唔食了<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/96iEf56.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F96iEf56.png&h=63267da4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃金油炸鬼 好熱氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WRys9r1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWRys9r1.png&h=dec4c174&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n突然好想豆腐 雖然你係我飲過最難飲嘅豆漿 但我都決定飲晒你<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3tFCNeq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3tFCNeq.png&h=e350c4b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食飽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好似無食過嘢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後祝大家 情人節快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c27aa8281f39a410b027d38de8677451a6fabfec","tid":1021713,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T12:17:44.000Z","msg":"肩兒生日快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8a0814a63dd7b1b9989b12a80e77badea0f8acc","tid":1021713,"uid":220305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T12:18:11.000Z","msg":"情人節快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fc8fdc509fd80953e3993ffe6c7de3ec03ac925","tid":1021713,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T12:18:35.000Z","msg":"真毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ff73ec49bd06c0112ca5ed2a591a9469ce66e1","tid":1021713,"uid":74214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T12:19:33.000Z","msg":"肩係快樂！"},{"pid":"2b28531ae8681c5f71e3d38b22c27017f6592502","tid":1021713,"uid":36435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T12:19:48.000Z","msg":"$44 全撚部麵粉黎"},{"pid":"f01edf6990d087c59af63f6e92e6d6ac41d2e967","tid":1021713,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T12:20:49.000Z","msg":"落單果陣講得出個餐名已經好犀利"},{"pid":"49aaccc567d2d09f14e7c3a8d869f45ed478939c","tid":1021713,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T12:23:37.000Z","msg":"食垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f28f65f8c4ad66e89ec8116fcbc9847c12c71714","tid":1021713,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c27aa8281f39a410b027d38de8677451a6fabfec","tid":1021713,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"